:"75a4a6ce1b07d3b37ab1bbcaf256648aa46282b2","tid":1728452,"uid":236880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:06:18.000Z","msg":"#市民投稿 #將軍澳 #調景嶺 #坑口 #寶琳<br />\n【唔好阻我返工啊】<br />\n<br />\n上星期我而經成個星期無得返工喇，一定要守住呢幾個位啊！下面呢幾個位一旦塞咗嘅話，就成個將軍澳就會出唔到去架喇！如果加埋啲人玩塞鐵，咁你叫四十萬將軍澳人點返工啊！<br />\n<br />\n點解唔洗守迴旋處？因為迴旋處比較闊，即使有交通意外都好少會塞死。反而上將軍澳隧道多數係單線，一畀人搞就大鑊。就算無人搞，有少少交通意外，都會塞死成個將軍澳。寶琳個關鍵位係好多巴士嘅出口（例如98_ 690 694 798），但如果呢個位出事，巴士有機會去景林迴旋處再經坑口寶琳關鍵位走，所以呢個位都重要。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好搞上面啲關鍵位呀！即割架！ <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKnUwRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKnUwRH.jpg&h=1bf5a7c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d5493b73716779a697b629b0122aff89728bd72","tid":1728452,"uid":67940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc022e180cc297899472f3c5377d90ad5b23983","tid":1728452,"uid":244624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a79ea6f05561fbdece7d8c0d4fccd4e227d4a91","tid":1728452,"uid":67940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hzG2FvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhzG2FvS.jpg&h=95d8aa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上星期嘅大三罷好成功<br />\n一於食住個勢上 一齊罷佢老母<br />\n今晚早啲瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你若放棄 誰佑我城</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"其實要罷到幾時？ 成個月？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:09:37.000Z","msg":"你問個政府囉"},{"pid":"a326d6f07332c16311a50dc83bab0ca5308720ec","tid":1728452,"uid":5623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-